Paul G. TANIS, Appellant, v. Billie TANIS. No. 15452. United States Court of Appeals Third Circuit. Argued Jan. 18, 1966. Decided Feb. 9, 1966. Herman P. Weinberg, Philadelphia, Pa., for appellant. Steven A. Arbittier, Philadelphia, Pa. (Anthony S. Minisi, Philadelphia, Pa., Wolf, Block, Schorr and Solis-Cohen, Philadelphia, Pa., on the brief), for ap-pellee.

Before KALODNER, Chief Judge, and McLAUGHLIN and GANEY, Circuit Judges.

PER CURIAM:

On review of the record we find no error. The Order of the District Court dated May 3, 1965 will be affirmed.
